### Estos tests se ejecutan con la extensión REST Client (Huachao Mao)

### Variables (Asegúrate de que el puerto coincide con tu .env.dev)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### 0. Healthcheck del Servidor
GET {{baseUrl}}/ping
Accept: application/json

### 1. Registrar un Paciente (Power User)
POST {{baseUrl}}/patients
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "externalId": "USR-WA-001",
  "disabilityGrade": 69,
  "isQuotaParticipant": true,
  "consentAccepted": true
}

### 2. Enviar Micro-Evaluación EMA (Regla 20s)
POST {{baseUrl}}/ema
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "externalId": "USR-WA-001",
  "energy": 4,
  "tension": 8,
  "clarity": 5,
  "responseTimeMs": 14500
}